cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper presents a system for generating random scenes and rendering them from different viewpoints, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The focus on active perception suggests a potential connection to robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of verifiable properties and comparative performance evaluations suggests a potential connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
